      "@type": "Paragraph",
      "labels": [
        "Paragraph"
      ],
      "name": "Paragraph 1",
      "chunk_text": "**Context**: Persisted UI and workflow settings in the browser\n**Intent**: Provide stable, discoverable storage keys with a single source of truth\n**Directive**: Reference only canonical keys from `canvas/src/lib/config.ls.ts` (no magic strings). For plugin-owned keys, import keys from the plugin package (host must not hardcode).",
      "properties": {
        "text": "**Context**: Persisted UI and workflow settings in the browser\n**Intent**: Provide stable, discoverable storage keys with a single source of truth\n**Directive**: Reference only canonical keys from `canvas/src/lib/config.ls.ts` (no magic strings). For plugin-owned keys, import keys from the plugin package (host must not hardcode).",
        "order": 1,
        "charCount": 331
