    },
    {
      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-local-storage-document:list:108:3",
      "@type": "List",
      "labels": [
        "List"
      ],
      "name": "List 3",
      "chunk_text": "`static` (default) runs 2D D3 force layout to a bounded stable state and then freezes the simulation; rich-media/markdown overlays forward wheel/pan to Canvas to keep pan/zoom primary and avoid per-frame overlay recomputation; Graph Data Table and GraphTableDb ignore pure position-only updates and only sync on content changes or explicit commands.\n`interactive` keeps D3 force simulation running and allows full embedded overlay interactivity (iframes/images/videos/markdown blocks accept wheel/pointer events and do not forward to Canvas when safe) while still using revision+viewKey-gated sync and SSOT GraphData/layout keys.",
      "properties": {
        "order": 3
      },
      "metadata": {
        "parsedAt": "2026-05-24T02:20:56+00:00",
        "source": "knowgrph_parser.graph_builder",
        "codebaseRoot": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph",
