        "sourceSentence": "`static` (default) runs 2D D3 force layout to a bounded stable state and then freezes the simulation; rich-media/markdown overlays forward wheel/pan to Canvas to keep pan/zoom primary and avoid per-frame overlay recomputation; Graph Data Table and GraphTableDb ignore pure position-only updates and only sync on content changes or explicit commands.",
        "temporalMarker": "then",
        "modality": "",
        "negation": false
      },
